        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer116300663" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7924396941908943520">The perfect novel.<br/><br/>Ingenious in its pace &amp; tone, the plot unravels in a peculiar, non-linear way, easily enviable by even the most capable of MAJOR writers. Perhaps because it is more like a meaty novella about star-crossed lovers, hidden intentions, and the war of &quot;the classes&quot; that it makes it&apos;s powerful, jarring punch to the gut.<br/><br/>I LooooVE this book. It&apos;s elegant, both prophetic and historic, &amp; very very adult.</span>
  <span id="freeText7924396941908943520" style="display:none">The perfect novel.<br /><br />Ingenious in its pace &amp; tone, the plot unravels in a peculiar, non-linear way, easily enviable by even the most capable of MAJOR writers. Perhaps because it is more like a meaty novella about star-crossed lovers, hidden intentions, and the war of "the classes" that it makes it's powerful, jarring punch to the gut.<br /><br />I LooooVE this book. It's elegant, both prophetic and historic, &amp; very very adult.</span>
